=== v3.0.5 ===
Fixes:
- Fixed render issue with parachutes
Additions:
- Added ICBM mod API
- Added hook into Universal Electricity

=== v3.0 ===
Changes:
- Updated to 1.6.2
- Changed "Turbo Model Thingy not installed" error message to reduce confusion
- teams.dat now saves in the Flan folder
- Packs now have a resource pack layout instead
- Teams help info is now shown in pages
- Mod is now packaged in a jar file
- Packs can now be loaded as zip files
- Improved WW2 gun and scope names and textures
- Changed bullet drop stats in Flan's packs
- Rewrote the laws of physics
- Rewrote vehicle damage mechanics
- Tons more
Fixes:
- Crosshairs properly locked in mouse control mode
Additions:
- Added missing angle for trailers
- Added option to rotate gunner with turret
- Added an NMT element to allow modifying corners of a box with x/y/z
- Added Nerf gamemode, armour, classes, guns etc
- Added grenades, proximity mines etc
- Added repair tools and medkits
- Added parachutes
- Loads more
Removals:
- Properties file

=== v2.3.2 ===
Changes:
- Increased propellor spin speed
- Planes no longer moveable by entities
- Removed mouse control toggle for vehicles
Fixes:
- Fixed tank barrels facing the wrong way when spawned
- Fixed camera view distance change for third person
- Fixed plane pitch switching upon reloading map
- Fixed a critical dupe exploit
- Fixed various team spawn issues
- Fixed trapezoid textures sheering along triangle edges
- Fixed LoadIntoGun and MaxStackSize incompatibility
- Fixed mouse control option getting stuck
- Fixed light levels not affecting scope brightness
- Fixed reload recoil with LoadIntoGun
- Fixed recoil with LoadIntoGun and no spare ammo
- Fixed glitchy plane movement with players in certain locations
- MGs drop smart stacks when smart stacks are enabled
Additions:
- Added Forge mod information files
- Added roll buttons, default to \ and X
- Added spinning wheels for vehicles
- Added toggleable plane wings, doors and gear to planes/vehicles. Buttons J, K and L
- Added config option to planes for parked position, planes spawn in paked position
- Added Trim/Park key "O" to reset plane position to parked or neutral
- Added option to restrict access to plane inventories during flight
- Added FlexBox and FlexTrapezoids to TMT for pack makers
- Added scope time setting to guns
- Added ability to have AAGuns, Planes and Vehicles despawn after a configurable time
- Added map rotation for teams games
- Added Conquest gametype
- Added CTF gametype
